        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figs. 1–7. Stratiomys reducta, new species. Characters of adults: 1, male abdomen, dorsal view; 2–4, male genitalia: cerci, proctiger and epandrium (2), genital capsule (3), phallic complex (4); 5, female abdomen, dorsal view; 6, female head, lateral view; 7, female head, frontal view, antennae removed." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4508994/files/figure.png" .

